title: Kpeve Fetish Dancer
creator: Barry Bilderback
description: A female dancer in the Kpeve village is seen displaying the physical embodiment of the transpossetion practice evidenced by chalk on the face, the staw skirt, and the ceremonial knife she wields. The knife is used to thrust into oneself in the straw skirt, often leaving scratches and abrasions.
